import { createApp } from 'vue/dist/vue.esm-bundler' import App from './App.vue' import AppDescription from './components/Description.vue' import AppGame from './components/Game.vue' import AppMenu from './components/Menu.vue' import * as VueRouter from 'vue-router' import axios from 'axios' import VueAxios from 'vue-axios' const app = createApp(App) //const FrontOffice = app.component('front-office', require('./scripts/FrontOffice').default) const BackOffice = app.component('back-office', require('./scripts/BackOffice').default) const routes = [ { path: '/', component: AppMenu}, { path: '/description', component: AppDescription }, { path: '/game', component: AppGame }, { path: '/services', component: {template: '
ouh
'} }, { path: '/administration', component: {template: BackOffice._component} } ] const router = VueRouter.createRouter({ history: VueRouter.createWebHistory(), routes } ) axios.defaults.baseURL = "http://localhost:8081" app.use(VueAxios,axios) app.use(router) app.mount('#app')
